The Voice Kids Australia - Season 1, Episode 6




The Battles Rounds #1

The blind auditions are over and now it's time for the Voice Kids teams to battle.Each coach has 15 talented singers, but only five will go through to the sing-offs.Unlike the adult series, the Voice Kids are put into trios and are mentored as a mini group.




Original Air Date: 23-Jul-2014
